titles.title: To reduce temporarily the duty on Cyfluthrin (Baythroid).

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary: 4/27/2005--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to reduce, through December 31, 2008, the duty on Cyano-(4-fluoro-3-phenoxyphenyl)methyl-3-(2,2-dichloroethenyl)-2,2- dimethylcyclopropanecarboxylate (Cyfluthrin (Baythroid)).
